story.title: Black Eyed Boy
story.storyDescription: Justin: Danny I think there is something seriously wrong with Jean-Paul

author.bio: Peter Petkovsek is a Columbia University School of the Arts graduate. Originally from Slovenia, he spends his time directing, writing and creating around the world.

messages.text: Danny I think there is something seriously wrong with Jean-Paul
Yeah … I think he killed someone!!
Dude WHAT? Did you see him??
Remember the kid who died last week
Joey? But that was a suicide …
Yeah but the day before I saw something really weird …
So what, he was a new kid, that’s normal
Jean-Paul just looked back at Joey in this really creepy way
No seriously - his eyes went completely BLACK for a second
You know, not just the little dot at the center, but the WHOLE EYE
Black as night … I felt cold all of a sudden
Is this your idea of a joke? Someone died dude
I know! But I’ve been watching Jean-Paul since then
He’s really strange ... Other kids just sort of avoid him
Well he’s new and foreign, that’s why!
It’s like there is some sort of dark energy around him
Sounds like a bunch of bullsh*t to me
BUT I SAW HIM DO IT AGAIN
Yesterday. That girl from Oklahoma, Jeannette
Yeah. I think he tried to ask her on a date, and she refused and laughed
And his eyes turned BLACK, for a second
I called her to see if she was ok but there was no answer
So I’m following Jean-Paul right now
My Mom just came in, she had a call from the principal
She slit her wrists this morning …
I really liked her … We only have school after lunch today
But what can we do? It’s not like anyone would believe that story
Wait, did you say you were following him?
WHAT? Dude, if this is true, you should stay away from him
I mean, this is some supernatural sh*t
Let’s just call the police or something
You said it – no one will believe us
I’m walking down the street after him
Jeez Justin why don’t you just watch him at school
He turned into an alley hold on
Justin STOP this you’ll get hurt!
He saw me. It was a trap. I turned the corner and there he was
Danny … That means I’m cursed now … I feel weird … kinda sad
No! You can prove yourself that this isn’t real!
Hold on getting on bus. I’ll see you at school later anyway … if I get there
I’m in school, where are you?
There you are!! You freaked me out. Feel what?
I just … don’t want to live anymore
It’s making me walk up the stairs to the roof
Omg Justin don’t do anything stupid
Listen! I’m trying to hold on
You have to do something for me
Yes. It’s dangerous, but you need to do it
Because I just stepped on the roof and I can’t make myself turn back
Insult him, but make sure you’re close to the bathroom door
Then run into the bathroom as fast as you can
And when he walks in, duck
Something is pulling me right to the edge of the roof
I’m standing on the edge of the roof Danny
He walked into the bathroom and looked at me and I ducked…
and he saw himself in the mirror just as his eyes went black
He just turned and ran up the stairs
I got out to the courtyard just in time to see him jump from the roof of the gym…
And the curse broke! I can move again! Back downstairs. The dread is gone!
YOU DID IT, you tricked him into cursing himself!
Wow. How did you know it would work?
I didn’t … But I realized he somehow does it with his eyes … so he could do it to himself maybe as well.
But you’re the one who actually did it!
No one will believe us though
We’ll make them, Danny. We’ll do it
